<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Player Info | SMLY Casino</title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/img/logo/headlogo.png" type="image/x-icon">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('header') %>
    <main class="main">
        <section class="section">
            <div class="section__content">
                <div class="section__logo">
                    <div class="section__logoImg">
                        <img class="section__img" src="/img/logo/headlogocards.png" alt="SMLY gambler with cards">
                    </div>
                    <span class="section__logoTitle"><strong>High</strong> or <strong>Low</strong></span>
                </div>
                <p class="section__p">
                    This is a simple little game you can play up to 10 rounds per deck. We will show you a random card
                    and the only thing you need to do is guess, if the next card will be higher or lower. The Ace is the lowest
                    and the King is the highest.Guess correctly and the house pays you the submitted value. Oh and If there is a draw... the house wins ðŸ˜Ž
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="section">
            <div class="section__content">
                <span class="section__title">Let's Play!</span>
                <div class="section__innerContent">
                    <div class="section__text section__information"> 
                        <div class="player__info">
                            <span class="player__stats"><strong class="section__strong">Player:</strong><%= player["username"] %></span>
                            <span class="player__stats"><strong class="section__strong">Current Amount:</strong><%= player["currentFunds"] %></span>
                            <span class="player__stats"><strong class="section__strong">Current Winnings:</strong><%= parseFloat(player["currentWinnings"]) %></span>
                            <span class="player__stats"><strong class="section__strong">Total Amount:</strong><%= totalAmount %></span>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="gamecorner__message">
                            <span class="message__label">Game Log</span>
                            <div class="message">
                               <p class="message__text"><% if(msg){%><%=msg%><%}%></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="section__game">
                        <div class="highlow">
                            <div class="highlow__imgContainer">
                                <img class="highlow__img" src= <%= card.getImgPath() %> alt="<%= (card.toString()) %>"/>
                            </div>
                            <div class="highlow__deck">
                                <img class="highlow__img" src= <%= card.backimage %> alt="<%= (card.toString()) %>"/>
                            </div>
                      
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="highlow__interactions">
                    <form class="section__form highlow__form" action="/games/highorlow" method="POST">
                        <label class="section__label" for="amount">Betting Amount</label>
                        <input class="section__input" type="number" placeholder="0" name="amount" min="1" id="amount" max="<%= totalAmount %>" required><span class="currency">SMLY</span>
                    
                        <div class="radio__group">
                            <label class="section__label">Higher:
                                <input type="radio" name="highlow" value="<%= (card.getPureRank()+1 ) %>" id="radio__higher" required>
                            </label>
                            <label class="section__label">Lower:
                                <input  type="radio" name="highlow" value="<%= (card.getPureRank()-1) %>" id="radio__lower">
                            </label>
                        </div>
                        <button s class="submit__button highlow__button section__button" type="submit">Make a bet</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
       
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    
    <%- include('footer') %>
    <script src="/scripts/highlow.js"></script>
</body>
</html>